        <Parent_String>temples by location or context [300007614], temples (buildings) [300007595], religious buildings [300007391], religious structures [300120364], ceremonial structures [300263489], single built works by function [300004894], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
